{"data":[{"date":"15:02 07/07","title":"C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/cdv-nam-dinh-dai-nao-san-thien-truong-nguoi-trong-cuoc-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee7 CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u1eabn HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1n gi\u1eadn d\u1eef c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi\u00a0C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng 18 V-League di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 6/7, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c 2-3. Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, cho r\u1eb1ng t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e0n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n \u0111\u00f2i '\u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7' v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/150207-3.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh\u00a0\u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t may v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh Nguy\u1ec5n T\u00e2n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng hay.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u00e2n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1ecf s\u00f3t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, l\u00e0m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ee1 v\u1ee5n, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i. V\u1ecb \u201cvua \u00e1o \u0111en\u201d c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc khi r\u00fat th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u1ede nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra b\u1ee9c x\u00fac cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao bi\u1ec7n cho s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i ra \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u, b\u1edfi c\u00e1i g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 hai m\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\u201d, \u00f4ng T\u00e2n Anh ph\u00e2n tr\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n thi\u00ean v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u00d4ng Th\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean 'c\u01a1n th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9' c\u1ee7a NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u00e0nh Nam. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 2000 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e1n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u1ecbt k\u00edn c\u00e1c l\u1ed1i ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cnh\u1ed1t\u201d t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch SLNA v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p. Ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfng, c\u00f4ng an m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1002","checkdouble":"190610"},{"date":"15:15 07/07","title":"Gareth Southgate l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/gareth-southgate-la-chia-khoa-cho-thanh-cong-cua-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2>Southgate l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang v\u1edbi Colombia, \u0110T Anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup. C\u00f2n t\u00ednh trong m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tham d\u1ef1, h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 6/7 l\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 s\u01b0 t\u1eed gi\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft l\u1ea1i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sau khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Colombia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang, gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebf th\u1eeba trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1edfi HLV Gareth Southgate khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trung v\u1ec7 John Stones cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Gareth lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb r\u1ea5t b\u1ed5 \u00edch v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate\" title=\"Gareth Southgate\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/gareth-southgate-la-chia-khoa-cho-thanh-cong-cua-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Gareth \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng trong 2 n\u0103m v\u1eeba qua, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u00f4ng nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, tinh th\u1ea7n, kh\u00e1t khao gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian b\u00ean nhau tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, \u0110T Anh c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng Gareth l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Stones chia s\u1ebb, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u1edfi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Gareth r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 g\u1ea7n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. \u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&quot;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-ibra-buong-loi-thach-thuc-hai-huoc-voi-beckham-421-190568.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-ibra-buong-loi-thach-thuc-hai-huoc-voi-beckham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-ibra-buong-loi-thach-thuc-hai-huoc-voi-beckham-421-190568.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh, Ibra bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Beckham</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 36 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ibra \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng khai tr\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-77-goi-giac-mo-ve-421-190574.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-77-goi-giac-mo-ve-421-190574.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7): G\u1ecdi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup &ndash; Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ecba t\u1ed1i cao \u0111\u00f3 su\u1ed1t g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 nay. Gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i duy...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1001","checkdouble":"190611"},{"date":"15:35 07/07","title":"Southgate: \u201cAnh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/southgate-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-anh-vs-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 chung cu\u1ed9c. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Selecao \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/275411/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\nSai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Tite</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, Brazil ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan, Selecao Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Tite \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb HLV Tite. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Brazil-roi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho \u0110T B\u1ec9 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eddi gian trong vi\u1ec7c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Selecao. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2002 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 'd\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1' l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9, HLV Tite b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n 4-3-3 cho Brazil v\u1edbi Neymar c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Coutinho c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Renato Augusto \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 thanh tho\u00e1t v\u00e0 m\u1edf ra nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m cho 'nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba'.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1961 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 khung thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Gabriel Jesus, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Selecao.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea1i cho William c\u00f2n c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c '\u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh' cho Neymar. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Brazil m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn h\u01a1n. Song tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, tam t\u1ea5u m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Selecao ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Brazil-bi-loai-khoi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Tite c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 trong cay \u0111\u1eafng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesus t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 duy\u00ean trong nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung phong c\u1eafm. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i cho ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Man City khi anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Brazil c\u0169ng t\u00ea li\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t Willian g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng cho t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng th\u00eam v\u00e0o b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y, HLV Tite m\u1edbi tung Douglas Costa v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino v\u00e0o s\u00e2n song th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Brazil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eeda sai sau 2 b\u00e0n thua ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu HLV Tite \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Firmino v\u00e0 Douglas Costa s\u1edbm h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, ho\u1eb7c ch\u00ed \u00edt l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190565.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng mang t\u00ean Neymar</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tin c\u1eady Casemiro v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 trong khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh, Fernandinho l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 't\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3' v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec1n khi\u1ebfn Brazil b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Neymar, si\u00eau sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Brazil v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh '\u0103n v\u1ea1' nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar an va\" title=\"Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/162539-11m.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tin 'ch\u00fa b\u00e9 ch\u0103n c\u1eebu' Neymar</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c Neymar li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil. N\u0103m l\u1ea7n b\u1ea3y l\u01b0\u1ee3t, c\u00e1c b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng b\u1ecb ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0110T B\u1ec9 song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh hay t\u1eeb t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video VAR.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c Neymar '\u0103n v\u1ea1' \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ch\u00fa b\u00e9 ch\u0103n c\u1eebu, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi khi m\u00e0 Brazil c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac Neymar n\u00ean nghi\u00eam t\u00fac nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u00f3i quen l\u00e0m k\u1ecbch s\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n tr\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup m\u00e0 l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 16 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba-421-190563.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/Brazil-roi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba-421-190563.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9: N\u1ed1i d\u00e0i c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 Samba</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Samba kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m khi thua \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi 1-7, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y Brazil c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n s\u1edbm h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 1-2. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tite tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1000","checkdouble":"190612"},{"date":"15:37 07/07","title":"Harry Maguire: \"Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u0103m n\u0103m c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/harry-maguire-anh-khong-duoc-bo-lo-co-hoi-tram-nam-co-mot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Harry Maguire ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maguire t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-77-goi-giac-mo-ve-421-190574.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Maguire ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Harry-Maguire-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire tin Anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHarry Maguire ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n qua \u0111\u00f3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\u00a0t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00fa treo b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Maguire tin Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u00ec l\u1ee3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Croatia ho\u1eb7c Nga \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire phat bieu ve DT Anh\" title=\"Harry Maguire ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/harry-maguire-anh-khong-duoc-bo-lo-co-hoi-tram-nam-co-mot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Nga v\u00e0 Crtoatia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Anh kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Harry Maguire kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m Anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u0103m n\u0103m c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t. Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eaft chiu nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPh\u00e1p ho\u1eb7c B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. N\u1ebfu l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"999","checkdouble":"190613"},{"date":"16:06 07/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ghen t\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/day-cap-doi-khien-messi-va-ronaldo-cung-phai-ghen-ti.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tu\u1ed5i ngo\u00e0i 30, Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0103n \u00fd. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi Uruguay, n\u01a1i Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u201csong s\u00e1t\u201d khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i e s\u1ee3.</h2><br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FL_Sei0BMQ4\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00f4n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. C\u00e1c CLB c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu, nh\u01b0ng \u0110TQG th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. Hai si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo hi\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArgentina c\u1ee7a Messi v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o h\u1ecd. V\u00e0 khi hai si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 n\u01a1i Argentina v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau khi ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eb3n Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Uruguay. H\u1ecd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0103n \u00fd. T\u1ea1i World cup 2018, Uruguay ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u00ec c\u00f3 5 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kia s\u1ebd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 \u201cc\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng\u201d kh\u00e9t ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Uruguay, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng xem clip tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 clip b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean Bongda24h,vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/fan-brazil-chet-lang-sau-that-bai-truoc-bi-461-190597.html\">Fan Brazil ch\u1ebft l\u1eb7ng sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cung-du-doan-tran-phap-vs-uruguay-voi-cho-tien-tri-461-190511.html\">C\u00f9ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 ti\u00ean tri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nu-viet-nam-100-nu-singapore-aff-cup-2018-325-190459.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 10-0 N\u1eef Singapore (AFF Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-41-u19-lao-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190441.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-1 U19 L\u00e0o (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-mexico-dien-lai-man-an-va-cua-neymar-461-190271.html\">C\u0110V Mexico di\u1ec5n l\u1ea1i m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<br>\r\nBongda24h.vn (TTVN) <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"998","checkdouble":"190615"},{"date":"16:50 07/07","title":"Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup: Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/brazil-roi-world-cup-tite-dang-trach-1-neymar-dang-trach-10.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 chung cu\u1ed9c. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Selecao \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/275411/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\nSai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Tite</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, Brazil ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan, Selecao Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Tite \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb HLV Tite. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Brazil-roi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho \u0110T B\u1ec9 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eddi gian trong vi\u1ec7c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Selecao. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2002 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 'd\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1' l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9, HLV Tite b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n 4-3-3 cho Brazil v\u1edbi Neymar c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Coutinho c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Renato Augusto \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 thanh tho\u00e1t v\u00e0 m\u1edf ra nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m cho 'nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba'.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1961 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 khung thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Gabriel Jesus, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Selecao.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea1i cho William c\u00f2n c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c '\u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh' cho Neymar. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Brazil m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn h\u01a1n. Song tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, tam t\u1ea5u m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Selecao ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Brazil-bi-loai-khoi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Tite c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 trong cay \u0111\u1eafng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesus t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 duy\u00ean trong nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung phong c\u1eafm. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i cho ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Man City khi anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Brazil c\u0169ng t\u00ea li\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t Willian g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng cho t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng th\u00eam v\u00e0o b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y, HLV Tite m\u1edbi tung Douglas Costa v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino v\u00e0o s\u00e2n song th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Brazil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eeda sai sau 2 b\u00e0n thua ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu HLV Tite \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Firmino v\u00e0 Douglas Costa s\u1edbm h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, ho\u1eb7c ch\u00ed \u00edt l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190565.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng mang t\u00ean Neymar</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Brazil r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tin c\u1eady Casemiro v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 trong khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh, Fernandinho l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 't\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3' v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec1n khi\u1ebfn Brazil b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Neymar, si\u00eau sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Brazil v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh '\u0103n v\u1ea1' nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar an va\" title=\"Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/162539-11m.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tin 'ch\u00fa b\u00e9 ch\u0103n c\u1eebu' Neymar</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c Neymar li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil. N\u0103m l\u1ea7n b\u1ea3y l\u01b0\u1ee3t, c\u00e1c b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng b\u1ecb ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0110T B\u1ec9 song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh hay t\u1eeb t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video VAR.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c Neymar '\u0103n v\u1ea1' \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ch\u00fa b\u00e9 ch\u0103n c\u1eebu, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi khi m\u00e0 Brazil c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac Neymar n\u00ean nghi\u00eam t\u00fac nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u00f3i quen l\u00e0m k\u1ecbch s\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n tr\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup m\u00e0 l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 16 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba-421-190563.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/Brazil-roi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba-421-190563.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9: N\u1ed1i d\u00e0i c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 Samba</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Samba kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m khi thua \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi 1-7, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y Brazil c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n s\u1edbm h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 1-2. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tite tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"997","checkdouble":"190617"},{"date":"16:33 07/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/truc-tiep-anh-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-thuy-dien-463-190618.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ANH VS TH\u1ee4Y \u0110I\u1ec2N</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"996","checkdouble":"190618"},{"date":"17:07 07/07","title":"LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Philippines 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/link-xem-truc-tiep-nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-philippines-19h00-ngay-77.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Philippines: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Philippines l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2><h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM VS N\u1eee PHILIPPINES</h2>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://mycujoo.tv/embed/593?id=21175\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Indonesia \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p 1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Singapore \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i \u00e9p s\u00e2n v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChung cu\u1ed9c \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i n\u1eef Sigapore v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 10-0. L\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV&nbsp;Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n n\u1eef Philippines d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 n\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong t\u1ea7m tay.<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"995","checkdouble":"190619"},{"date":"17:15 07/07","title":"B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Brazil v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft: \u201cCon dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i\u201d c\u1ee7a Martinez","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/bi-oai-hung-vao-ban-ket-con-dao-hai-luoi-cua-martinez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1ng trong c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t 45 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a thi\u00ean t\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Roberto Martinez</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf ph\u00fat 38, B\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Eden Hazard l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trung l\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Kevin De Bruyne, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ngay t\u1ee9c kh\u1eafc v\u1eabn h\u01a1i ch\u1eadm v\u00e0 l\u1ee1 nh\u1ecbp di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec b\u1edfi c\u00fa gi\u1eadt g\u00f3t th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Brazil k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi k\u00e9o v\u1ec1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, gi\u1ea3i nguy cho khung th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker trong h\u01a1i th\u1edf g\u1ea5p g\u00e1p, h\u1ed5n h\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Du-am-Brazil-vs-Bi-Chien-thang-nho-con-dao-hai-luoi-cua-Martinez-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9: De Bruyne k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn Selecao ngay t\u1eeb hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i, B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t Brazil trong t\u1ea7m tay. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p tam gi\u00e1c trong khi Selecao ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111u\u1ed5i theo nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. Quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb ng\u1eaft qu\u00e3ng khi Alisson tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o c\u1ee7a De Bruyne r\u1ed3i c\u00e1i flick ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Vincent Kompany t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c sau \u0111\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai ph\u00fat tr\u00f4i qua, v\u00e0 Brazil ch\u1ea1m ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c, bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng cho m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u0103m l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau 45 ph\u00fat \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ed1n n\u0103m. \u0110\u1ecf-v\u00e0ng-\u0111en qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1eafc m\u00e0u qu\u1ed1c k\u1ef3 khi\u1ebfn Selecao ph\u1ea3i b\u1ee7n r\u1ee7n tay ch\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, Tite \u0111\u1ed1c th\u00fac c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n trong hi\u1ec7p hai nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng. Thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i g\u00e2y ra b\u1edfi tam t\u1ea5u th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh ph\u00eda B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 kinh ho\u00e0ng r\u1ed3i. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0103n \u00fd gi\u1eefa t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, Hazard, De Bruyne v\u00e0 Lukaku r\u1eafp t\u00e2m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n Mineirazo sau b\u1ed1n n\u0103m \u1edf Kazan \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/170805-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9: Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf m\u1edbi nh\u1ea3y Samba \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, B\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee5 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea3y \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n khai sinh ra n\u00f3. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ai \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Lukaku c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i sang ph\u1ea3i, trong khi De Bruyne l\u00ean k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o trung t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f2n Hazard gi\u00e0y x\u00e9o h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Brazil. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, Fellaini ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea3 trong nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Selecao ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, v\u1eadt v\u00e3 ki\u1ebfm t\u00ecm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-ha-guc-brazil-hay-cam-on-premier-league-vi-the-he-vang-421-190575.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/luka.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-ha-guc-brazil-hay-cam-on-premier-league-vi-the-he-vang-421-190575.html\">B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Brazil: H\u00e3y c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Premier League v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nNeymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, trong khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 b\u00e1 v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, ng\u1edd v\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV 45 tu\u1ed5i gi\u0103ng ra \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5p li\u1ebfm su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Brazil. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">4-3-3 v\u1edbi Nacer Chadli \u00e1n ng\u1eef trung t\u00e2m bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a trong ch\u1edbp m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh kim c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi De Bruyne tung ho\u00e0nh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh. 3-4-3 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c c\u0169ng v\u1eady khi thu v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh 4-2-3-1 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Brazil v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Brazil v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Bi-ha-be-Brazil-vao-ban-ket-Con-dao-hai-luoi-cua-Martinez-hinh-anh-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9: Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n, Lukaku v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Man Utd mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm, trong khi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 hai l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a De Bruyne. M\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 tr\u00ed tu\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7p hai c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Martinez c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t khi v\u1edbi 45 ph\u00fat b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t Brazil \u0111i\u00ean cu\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u1edbi tung h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, B\u1ec9 s\u00fat 8 v\u00e0 Brazil s\u00fat 10. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, B\u1ec9 1 v\u00e0 Brazil 15.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Selecao t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean phong ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn Gabriel Jesus v\u1edbi \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 c\u1ee7a Lord Fred ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i, Roberto Firmino \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 sau 5 ph\u00fat v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, trong khi Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 Renato August b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n. C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f3a th\u00e1nh trong khung g\u1ed7 khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng cho nh\u1eefng Paulinho, Douglas Costa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Neymar \u1edf th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/170903-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9: Selecao \u0111i\u00ean cu\u1ed3ng d\u1ed3n \u00e9p nh\u1eb1m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi Augusto r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, Martinez d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh, kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbm t\u1ef1 tin th\u00e1i qu\u00e1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5m m\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3, r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc an to\u00e0n thay v\u00ec co c\u1ee5m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 n\u00f3. Ph\u00fat 83 m\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 Thomas Vermaelen m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brazil \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn s\u1edbm s\u1ee7a, thay v\u00ec d\u00f4ng d\u00e0i hy v\u1ecdng mong manh \u0111\u1ebfn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng cho t\u1edbi t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. K\u1ec3 ra s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Martinez b\u1ea5t lu\u1eadn ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh, t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 v\u1eady t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9 Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Martinez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil vs B\u1ec9: Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf s\u1ed1ng trong s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i \u1edf hi\u1ec7p hai v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eadn t\u00e2m h\u01a1n khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng cu\u1ed9c sau c\u00f9ng, k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i duy nh\u1ea5t su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. V\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 32 n\u0103m v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u1ed9ng m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng d\u00f9 cho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t h\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a HLV v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng vui s\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0ng l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n B\u1ec9, trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 trung l\u1eadp nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta, h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Brazil t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba-421-190563.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9: N\u1ed1i d\u00e0i c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 Samba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-roi-world-cup-tite-dang-trach-1-neymar-dang-trach-10-421-190617.html\">Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup: Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"994","checkdouble":"190620"},{"date":"17:26 07/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n phi th\u01b0\u1eddng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb9p Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-thuy-dien-va-du-doan-soi-keo-thuy-dien-vs-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara Arena.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng thua trong 90 ph\u00fat<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: H\u00f2a 0-0 (Anh th\u1eafng hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 ho\u1eb7c penalty) <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-thuy-dien-463-190618.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/truc-tiep-anh-vs-thuy-dien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-thuy-dien-463-190618.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 21h ng\u00e0y 7/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Samara Arena<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Anh 0.99*0:1/2*0.96 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u -0.99*2*0.92 \u00cdt</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-thuy-dien-va-du-doan-soi-keo-thuy-dien-vs-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 21h ng\u00e0y 7/7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 th\u1eddi th\u1ebf t\u1ea1o anh h\u00f9ng. \u0110T Anh mang t\u1edbi World Cup 2018 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, Tam s\u01b0 l\u1ea1i \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t xa v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho Tam s\u01b0. S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 g\u1ed3m 3 trung v\u1ec7 ban \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd song l\u1ea1i \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate\" title=\"Gareth Southgate\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/gareth-southgate-la-chia-khoa-cho-thanh-cong-cua-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Southgate c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho \u0110T&nbsp;Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t ph\u00eda sau, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Anh nh\u01b0 Kieran Trippier v\u00e0 Ashley Young c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Southgate c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a nguy\u00ean b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u01b0ng \u00fd Dele Alli, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t l\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao l\u1edbn. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i to\u00e0n n\u0103ng Alli Lingard k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng Jordan Henderson t\u1ea1o n\u00ean trung tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ef1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn cho Anh. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, ph\u00eda sau h\u1ecd c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 John Stones v\u00e0 Harry Maguire kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi Kyle Walker v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u00fat l\u1ea5n c\u1ea5n khi ch\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7, s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Stones v\u00e0 Maguire t\u1ea1i CLB m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd mang l\u00ean \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuyen Anh gianh chien thang\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/14.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f2n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Anh. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n c\u1ee5c, nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u01a1n l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao Zlatan Ibrahimovic l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ec9 sau Ph\u00e1p, tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi Nga. S\u00e1t VCK, \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi h\u1ecd g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Ibrahimovic. Nh\u01b0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Janne Andersson \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian ch\u1ee9ng minh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thuy Dien thang Mexico 3-0\" title=\"Thuy Dien thang Mexico 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-mexico-03-thuy-dien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng Ibra d\u1ea7n b\u1ecf \u0111i s\u1ef1 \u1ef7 l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 thay v\u00ec tri\u1ec3n khai xung quanh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 h\u00e0o nho\u00e1ng, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0, Mexico 3-0 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat \u0110\u1ee9c 1-2 b\u1edfi kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc th\u0103ng hoa nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos. T\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8, s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 1-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HARRY KANE  Sat thu vo hinh cua Tam Su 1\" title=\"HARRY KANE  S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/kane-dt-anh-giong-nhu-gia-dinh-dich-thuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Kane</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T Anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Harry Kane trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong 16 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh Colombia v\u00f2ng 1/8, ch\u1ec9 2 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 penalty th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Kane trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng Lingard r\u1ed3i Sterling v\u1eabn \u0111ang phung ph\u00ed c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n tin Vardy ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t. H\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 suy gi\u1ea3m v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Andersson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng thua trong 90 ph\u00fat<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: H\u00f2a 0-0 (Anh th\u1eafng hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 ho\u1eb7c penalty) <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"993","checkdouble":"190621"},{"date":"09:13 07/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Courtois n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nguoi-hung-courtois-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda anh sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>Courtois s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, \u0111\u01b0a B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Courtois t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, \u0111\u01b0a B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/nguoi-hung-courtois-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Courtois l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Chelsea. V\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge tr\u1edf n\u00ean lung lay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span> t\u1ea1i Kazan, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Courtois t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t pha c\u1ee9u thua quan tr\u1ecdng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 ng\u0103n Neymar ghi b\u00e0n cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Neymar th\u00edch c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng theo c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ai v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u0103ng hoa. Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb b\u00e9 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng thua tr\u1eadn th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs B\u1ec9:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190565.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"992","checkdouble":"190578"},{"date":"09:06 07/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-da-nang-vs-hai-phong-17h00-ngay-77-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (V\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 77 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 77 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/shb-da-nang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: 3-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n N\u1ed9i FC (2-5) v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (2-4). T\u1edbi v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng h\u00f2a Thanh H\u00f3a 3-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo l\u1eafng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 3 tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 12 l\u1ea7n. Sau 17 v\u00f2ng, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018 (31).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 V-League, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng to\u00e0n thua c\u1ea3 9 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. 6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf V-League, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111ang h\u01a1n \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 3 b\u1eadc tr\u00ean BXH (\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 10 v\u1edbi 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m). H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111ang d\u1ea7n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i khi 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA v\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng thua 2, h\u00f2a 1 \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba qua \u1edf V-League, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh nh\u01b0 Stevens hay Fagan c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp c\u1ee7a hai ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Fagan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: V\u00f5 Huy To\u00e0n, \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: Thanh B\u00ecnh, Nh\u1eadt T\u00e2n, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ec5, Ewonder, Thanh Th\u1ecbnh, Minh T\u00e2m, Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng, Thanh H\u1ea3i, Vi\u1ebft Th\u1eafng, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Yao Hermann.<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ho\u00e0ng Nam, Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ho\u00e0ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Th\u00e0nh Long, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, V\u0103n Ph\u00fa, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, Stevens, Fagan.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"991","checkdouble":"190580"},{"date":"09:15 07/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-thanh-hoa-19h00-ngay-77-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (V\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a 19h00 ng\u00e0y 77 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a 19h00 ng\u00e0y 77 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/sai-gon-vs-thanh-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a: 3-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 5 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u00f3 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ngo\u1ea1i binh Faye v\u00e0 Ofere \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 13 trong s\u1ed1 25 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 (TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh) \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, CLB c\u1ee7a HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Trong 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 13 trong s\u1ed1 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u00e0 Da Sylva. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mauritania \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 16 tr\u1eadn, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 trong danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 sau Oseni c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p h\u01a1n 1/3 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i V-League, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: V\u0103n Phong (GK), Ng\u1ecdc H\u00e0o, V\u0103n Ng\u1ecd, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ee3i, Ng\u1ecdc Duy, Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean, Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n Tri\u1ec1n, Anh V\u0169, V\u0169 T\u00edn, Da Sylva.<br>\r\n+ Thanh H\u00f3a: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (GK), \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, V\u0103n Nam, Minh T\u00f9ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Faye, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"990","checkdouble":"190581"},{"date":"09:40 07/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Uruguay b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau sai l\u1ea7m t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/thu-mon-uruguay-bi-chi-trich-sau-sai-lam-te-hai-truoc-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Fernando Muslera sau sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Gary Neville h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Gary Neville h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/thu-mon-uruguay-bi-chi-trich-sau-sai-lam-te-hai-truoc-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn Uruguay thua Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raphael Varane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u1edf ph\u00fat 61 khi Muslera kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i hi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Griezmann.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Atletico Madrid \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eb3ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Muslera. Thay v\u00ec b\u1eaft g\u1ecdn, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng ra ngo\u00e0i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng b\u1eadt l\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u1ed3i \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Muslera</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p</span>, Neville \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Uruguay. B\u1edfi n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u0129 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ngu ng\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9. N\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 bom.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i c\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ed3i. Th\u1eadt ra t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u00fa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a Muslera. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 tay l\u1ecdt ra kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMuslera \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 sai t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh. \u1ede tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi 100 c\u00fa s\u00fat nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ea3 100 qu\u1ea3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eb7t tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ef1c v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGriezmann \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-20-cua-phap-truoc-uruguay-421-190559.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 0-2 Ph\u00e1p (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"989","checkdouble":"190582"},{"date":"09:22 07/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-nga-vs-croatia-1h00-ngay-87-co-hoi-nao-cho-chu-nha.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tan r\u00e3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ed1i x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 ngh\u0129a \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u v\u00e0o th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 90 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00e9o theo m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong khu v\u1ef1c, m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1ch ra t\u1eeb sau s\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u loay hoay t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh huy ho\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 87) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 87) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Nga-vs-Croatia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia: Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y, Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t. T\u00e1ch ra t\u1eeb Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169, Croatia \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 1998, k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean &quot;Vatreni&quot; tham d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi kh\u1ed1i XHCN t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng World Cup 2018 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Vi\u1ec7c Nga vs Croatia ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u00fap m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. V\u1edbi Croatia, th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Luka Modric c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Davor Suker t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f2n 20 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966, khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean X\u00f4.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Nga r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao nh\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic - nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u hi\u1ec7n nay.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga va Croatia deu so huu nhung trung phong co the hinh an tuong la Dzyuba va Mandzukic.\" title=\"Nga v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung phong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Dzyuba v\u00e0 Mandzukic.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/dyuba-vs-mandzukic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nga v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung phong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Dzyuba v\u00e0 Mandzukic.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1ed1ng nhau khi \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u sang bi\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 uy hi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung phong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Atem Dzyuba (Nga) v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic (Croatia).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Croatia c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn hai d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, 4 trong s\u1ed1 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i to\u00e1n c\u1ea7n HLV Cherchesov gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Fisht Olympic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Nga v\u00e0 Croatia t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau 3 l\u1ea7n. Hai trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2008 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng bnf th\u1eafng. Tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 cho Croatia \u1edf giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11/2015.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Croatia ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y (8) ngang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2006 v\u00e0 2014 c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Nga c\u00f3 10 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng trong hai tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, 1 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n (Dzyuba vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* 10 trong 12 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ebfn trong hi\u1ec7p hai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup cho \u0110T Croatia, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m Davor Suker (6).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga:</strong> Alan Dzagoev, Yuri Zhirkov ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Croatia:</strong> Ivan Strinic ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Akinfeev - 2.Fernandes, 3.Kutepov, 4.Ignashevich, 13.Kudryashov - 8.Gazinskiy, 11.Zobnin - 19.Samedov, 17.Golovin, 6.Cheryshev - 22.Dzyuba</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Croatia (4-5-1): </strong>23.Subasic - 2.Vrsaljko, 21.Vida, 6.Lovren, 3.Strinic - 18.Rebic, 10.Modric, 11.Brozovic, 7.Rakitic, 4.Perisic - 17.Mandzukic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Nga 1-1 Croatia (Nga th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nga vs Croatia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/073513-Nga-vs-Croatia-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-5-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Nga v\u00e0 Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-chiec-giay-vang-goi-ten-ai-421-190348.html\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea-421-190313.html\">H\u00e0ng hot tuy\u1ec3n Nga ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/luka-modric-ngon-co-dau-cua-nguoi-croatia-389-190104.html\">Luka Modric: Ng\u1ecdn c\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-modric-hay-rakitic-linh-hon-cua-croatia-la-ai-421-189917.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Modric hay Rakitic, linh h\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 ai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-croatia-vs-dan-mach-463-190116.html\">Croatia 1-1 (pen 3-2) \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (KT): L\u00ednh ch\u00ec b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i d\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"988","checkdouble":"190583"}]}